<p class="note">
	{tr}Show files to be downloaded. If set, <kbd>content_id</kbd> restricts the list to given file gallery, <kbd>user_id</kbd> to a given user.{/tr}
	<br />
	<span class="example">{tr}Example:{/tr} <kbd>content_id=33&amp;sort_mode=last_modified</kbd></span>
</p>

<dl>
	<dt class="param"><kbd>content_id</kbd></dt>
	<dd><em>{tr}Numeric{/tr}</em></dd>

	<dt class="param"><kbd>user_id</kbd></dt>
	<dd><em>{tr}Numeric{/tr}</em></dd>

	<dt class="param"><kbd>sort_mode</kbd></dt>
	<dd><em>{tr}String{/tr}</em></dd>
	<dd>random, created, hits, last_modified</dd>
</dl>
